result.name: Fairwood

reviews.text:
You need to negotiate two flights of stairs because the restaurant is located on the first floor of Kyoto Plaza building (in Hong Kong, 1/F is the floor above the ground floor).

Similar to all Fairwood branches elsewhere, the available menu choices are posted on a sidewall in front of the cashier. Since I had a late dinner here, there are not too many diners.  I was handed an electronic gadget - instead of queueing-up at the kitchen counter to receive my order.

A server came to my table with the meal minutes later, having no need to get it myself.

Food was served hot and I enjoyed the pork cutlet curry on rice with veggies.  The meat is tender and juicy, and the thickness is quite right.
Fast, easy and cheap. Nice
Safest choice of quick meal for first time HK visitors.
good price for tasty meal

No comment on food for chain restaurant.  
This Fairwood is not huge, but still can accommodate lot of customers during lunch peak hours.  And tables are packed as usual.
They have lot of tables with street view, and its comfortable for dining under the sun and the bust street view

result.name: 大快活

reviews.text: 我收回上次有關工作流程的評論，這間前台人更少（只有两個）但很暢順，可能比大家樂快，清枱也勤快，唯一美中不足近門口不夠冷氣，客人都湧入店埋邊

You need to negotiate two flights of stairs because the restaurant is located on the first floor of Kyoto Plaza building (in Hong Kong, 1/F is the floor above the ground floor).

Similar to all Fairwood branches elsewhere, the available menu choices are posted on a sidewall in front of the cashier. Since I had a late dinner here, there are not too many diners.  I was handed an electronic gadget - instead of queueing-up at the kitchen counter to receive my order.

A server came to my table with the meal minutes later, having no need to get it myself.

Food was served hot and I enjoyed the pork cutlet curry on rice with veggies.  The meat is tender and juicy, and the thickness is quite right.
銅鑼灣區便宜又清潔食肆已很少，只是座位不多。
這分店的經理帶領員工好有團隊合作精神,而且非常有效率·衛生及禮貌都算合格
部份分店欠無障礙通道，食物一般
